{"type": "article", "id": 22513, "title": "类似巨松结构的木桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-19T07:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120035iMcpT3fJvmXSEz0l.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这张木桌来自西班牙设计师 Silvia Ceñal，它的特殊之处在于桌腿与铰接支座之间的关节设计。设计师称灵感源于法国朗德森林里的巨松，它的树干上有粗壮垂直相交的枝条。对应到这张桌子，较粗的桌腿就是树干，两根较细的横梁支撑则是上枝条，给人轻盈而优雅的视觉感受，<a href=\"http://www.silviacenal.com/#/foret-table/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120033Tl3Qb4qa8WtH70u6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120034FkJ2IhSpl7bTLGKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031200347sZ6f0udmicQPM3V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 375px; width: 375px; left: 560px; top: 1295px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120035VoSY8JTnaiMA3Xvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}